caption.p: Apoptotic effect of TCEO treatment on MCF-7 cells. (A) Dot plots of MCF-7 cells treated with 12.5 and 25 µg/mL of TCEO for 24 h. A1: necrotic cells, A2: late apoptotic cells, A3: Viable cells, and A4: early apoptotic cells. (B) The bar graphs show the percentages of viable, early, late and necrotic cells for non-treated and treated MCF-7 cells.
